"'''After the Rain'''" is the sixth single by Australian hard rock group [[The Angels (Australian band)|the Angels]], released in 1978 off the album ''[[Face to Face (The Angels album)|Face to Face]]''.<ref name="discogs">{{cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/The-Angels-The-Tour-EP/release/6262935|publisher=discogs.com|title=The Angels - The Tour EP (Vinyl) at Discogs|accessdate=2016-12-28}}</ref> "After the Rain" first charted on the [[ARIA Charts]] on November 27, 1978, peaked at number 52 during a 21-week run.<ref name="australianmusicdatabase">{{cite web|url=http://www.australianmusicdatabase.com/recordings/after-the-rain-by-the-angels|publisher=australianmusicdatabase.com|title=After The Rain &#124; Australian Music Database|accessdate=2016-12-28}}</ref><ref name="guitaretab">{{cite web|url=http://www.guitaretab.com/a/angels/523.html|publisher=guitaretab.com|title=Angels - ( After The Rain tab ) |accessdate=2016-12-28}}</ref>
