'''Vitaly Lazarenko''' (1890–1939) was a [[Russians|Russian]]/[[Soviet Union|Soviet]] [[Acrobatics|acrobat]] know best for his acrobatic skills and use of political satire during events.<ref>{{cite web|title=Vitaly Lazarenko|url=http://www.answers.com/topic/vitaly-lazarenko|publisher=Oxford Encyclopedia of Theatre and Performance|accessdate=1 May 2011}}</ref>

He performed in the clown duo [[Bim Bom]].

